#StatsAZ gives per month mean of Leaf Bio Dry Weight (per m^2) and Standard Error

<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-output-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiXG48IS0tIHJuYi1zb3VyY2UtYmVnaW4gZXlKa1lYUmhJam9pWUdCZ2NseHVVM1JoZEhOQldpQThMU0JCWW05MlpWb2dKVDRsSUdkeWIzVndYMko1S0UxdmJuUm9LU0FsUGlVZ2MzVnRiV0Z5YVhObEtHMWxZVzQ5SUcxbFlXNG9Ra1JYS1N3Z2MyUWdQU0J6WkNoQ1JGY3BMQ0J1UFc0b0tTd2djMlU5YzJRdmMzRnlkQ2h1S1NrZ0pUNGxJRzExZEdGMFpTaEpSRDB4S1Z4dVUzUmhkSE5CV2lBOExTQmhjeTVrWVhSaExtWnlZVzFsS0ZOMFlYUnpRVm9wWEc1VGRHRjBjMEZhWEc1Z1lHQWlmUT09IC0tPlxuXG5gYGByXG5TdGF0c0FaIDwtIEFib3ZlWiAlPiUgZ3JvdXBfYnkoTW9udGgpICU+JSBzdW1tYXJpc2UobWVhbj0gbWVhbihCRFcpLCBzZCA9IHNkKEJEVyksIG49bigpLCBzZT1zZC9zcXJ0KG4pKSAlPiUgbXV0YXRlKElEPTEpXG5TdGF0c0FaIDwtIGFzLmRhdGEuZnJhbWUoU3RhdHNBWilcblN0YXRzQVpcbmBgYFxuXG48IS0tIHJuYi1zb3VyY2UtZW5kIC0tPlxuIn0= -->

StatsAZ <- AboveZ %>% group_by(Month) %>% summarise(mean= mean(BDW), sd = sd(BDW), n=n(), se=sd/sqrt(n)) %>% mutate(ID=1)
StatsAZ <- as.data.frame(StatsAZ)
StatsAZ

#StatsBZ subsets data for monthly mean below bdw (mutate(ID=1) used to ensure geom_line connects to datapoints)

<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-output-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiXG48IS0tIHJuYi1zb3VyY2UtYmVnaW4gZXlKa1lYUmhJam9pWUdCZ2NseHVVM1JoZEhOQ1dpQThMU0JDWld4dmQxb2dKVDRsSUdkeWIzVndYMko1S0UxdmJuUm9LU0FsUGlVZ2MzVnRiV0Z5YVhObEtHMWxZVzQ5SUcxbFlXNG9Ra1JYS1N3Z2MyUWdQU0J6WkNoQ1JGY3BMQ0J1UFc0b0tTd2djMlU5YzJRdmMzRnlkQ2h1S1NrZ0pUNGxJRzExZEdGMFpTaEpSRDB4S1Z4dVUzUmhkSE5DV2x4dVlHQmdJbjA9IC0tPlxuXG5gYGByXG5TdGF0c0JaIDwtIEJlbG93WiAlPiUgZ3JvdXBfYnkoTW9udGgpICU+JSBzdW1tYXJpc2UobWVhbj0gbWVhbihCRFcpLCBzZCA9IHNkKEJEVyksIG49bigpLCBzZT1zZC9zcXJ0KG4pKSAlPiUgbXV0YXRlKElEPTEpXG5TdGF0c0JaXG5gYGBcblxuPCEtLSBybmItc291cmNlLWVuZCAtLT5cbiJ9 -->

StatsBZ <- BelowZ %>% group_by(Month) %>% summarise(mean= mean(BDW), sd = sd(BDW), n=n(), se=sd/sqrt(n)) %>% mutate(ID=1)
StatsBZ

#Total Shoot count monthly mean and SE

StatsTSC <- ABZ %>% group_by(Month) %>% summarise(mean= mean(TSC, na.rm=TRUE), sd = sd(TSC, na.rm=TRUE), n=n(), se=sd/sqrt(n)) %>%  mutate(ID=1)

ggplot(StatsTSC, aes(x=Month, y=mean, group = ID))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_line()+
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=mean-se, ymax = mean+se, width=0.2))+
  labs(y=bquote(~\Shoot Density\~(\Shoot\~m^\-2\)))+

#subsets data for only April and acquires mean of Above, Below, and Total BDW and the ratio of leaf to rhizome (Unable to calculate SE as Dry weight Above and Below measured seperately and not tied with Sample ID and Replicate)

AprilAB <- subset(ABZ, ABZ$Month == \April\) %>% select(-Replicate, -Sample_ID, -TSC) %>%  group_by(SGP)%>% mutate(ID=row_number()) %>%  pivot_wider(names_from = SGP, values_from = BDW) %>% ungroup() %>% select(-\NA\) %>% group_by(Month) %>% summarise(Above=mean(Above), Below=mean(Below)) %>% mutate(TotalBDW= Above+Below, ABRat= Above/Below)
AprilAB



<!-- rnb-output-end -->

#Subset of data for all months OTHER than April, and keeps "Above" and "Below" BDW with respective SampleID and replicate

<!-- rnb-text-end -->

ABR1 <- subset(ABZ, ABZ$Month != \April\) %>% select(-TSC, -ID)  %>% pivot_wider( names_from = SGP, values_from = BDW) %>% mutate(SampRep= paste(Sample_ID, Replicate)) %>% mutate(TotalBDW=Above+Below, ABRat= Above/Below) %>% group_by(Month) %>% select(-Sample_ID, -Replicate)
ABR1

#Finds mean of Total BDW and SE (TSE) and mean of Leaf to Rhizome ratio (ABRat) and SE (RSE) 

<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-output-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiXG48IS0tIHJuYi1zb3VyY2UtYmVnaW4gZXlKa1lYUmhJam9pWUdCZ2NseHVRVUpTTWlBOExVRkNVakVnSlQ0bElITjFiVzFoY21selpTaFVVMFU5YzJRb1ZHOTBZV3hDUkZjcEwzTnhjblFvYmlncEtTd2dVbE5GUFhOa0tFRkNVbUYwS1M5emNYSjBLRzRvS1Nrc0lGUnZkR0ZzUWtSWFBXMWxZVzRvVkc5MFlXeENSRmNwTENCQlFsSmhkRDBnYldWaGJpaEJRbEpoZENrZ0tWeHVRVUpTTWx4dVlHQmdJbjA9IC0tPlxuXG5gYGByXG5BQlIyIDwtQUJSMSAlPiUgc3VtbWFyaXNlKFRTRT1zZChUb3RhbEJEVykvc3FydChuKCkpLCBSU0U9c2QoQUJSYXQpL3NxcnQobigpKSwgVG90YWxCRFc9bWVhbihUb3RhbEJEVyksIEFCUmF0PSBtZWFuKEFCUmF0KSApXG5BQlIyXG5gYGBcblxuPCEtLSBybmItc291cmNlLWVuZCAtLT5cbiJ9 -->

ABR2 <-ABR1 %>% summarise(TSE=sd(TotalBDW)/sqrt(n()), RSE=sd(ABRat)/sqrt(n()), TotalBDW=mean(TotalBDW), ABRat= mean(ABRat) )
ABR2

ggplot(ABR, aes(x=Month, y=TotalBDW, group=ID))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_line()+
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymax = TotalBDW+TSE, ymin=TotalBDW-TSE, width=0.2))+
  labs(y=bquote(~\Total Weight\~(g~m^\-2\)))+
  theme_classic()

```
ggplot(ABR, aes(x=Month, y=ABRat, group=ID))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_line()+
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymax = ABRat+RSE, ymin=ABRat-RSE, width=0.2))+
  labs(y=\A:B\)+
  theme_classic()

````
